Admin Assistant (Operations)

Responsibilities:
- Support day-to-day administrative support to the Operations department such as work schedule, renewal of driving license, traffic fines, etc
- Calculation of drivers’ monthly incentives
- Handling of customer enquiries, liaising with sales department for any ad-hoc cases
- Establish, build and maintain close working relations with drivers and other departments
- Other ad-hoc duties as and when assigned by reporting supervisor

Requirements:
- Possess at least Diploma in Business Administration or any related disciplines
- Good working knowledge in Microsoft Office applications especially in Microsoft Words/Excel
- Able to speak Mandarin so as to liaise with Chinese speaking associates
- Good interpersonal and communication skills
- Able to handle and manage ambiguity